budgie-welcome (0.6.0) bionic; urgency=medium

  * Bug-fix to display live booting information correctly in tabs
  * Remove custom CSS for adapta theme
  * Adapta theme now installs breeze cursor and papirus icons
  * latest translations
  * Fix crash when displaying version from command line (LP: #1721711)
  * Fix crash when graphics info cannot be found (LP: #1720623)
  * Add menu accessible .desktop files for themes and applets
  * Rename flat-plat to materia theme
  * Add budgie-extras applets
  * Add Ant theme and Pop theme
  * Add links to project websites for applets
  * Add recommendation for Dropbox
  * Drop recommendation for budgie-screenshot-applet
  * Headerbar GTK theming
  * Packaging Changes:
    - debian/control Bump standard version: No changes required
    - debian/control debhelper v11
    - debian/control corrected Vcs locations
    - debian/rules remove unneeded autoinstall override
    - debian/copyright: 2018 year change

